        <br/><br/>
        RoboCent reserves the right to disclose your information during the following instances:
        <br/><br/>
        <dd>
          During any legal action, including investigations by law enforcement, RoboCent reserves the right to disclose any and all information provided to RoboCent from any client. This information includes, but is not limited to, billing information, information on contacts as well as any personally identifiable information.
        </dd>
        <br/>
        <dd>
          In the event of a merger or acquisition, RoboCent reserves the right to pass on all available information to RoboCent's successor, parent company or other entity that acquires RoboCent.
        </dd>
      </div>

      <div class="divider_space_thin"></div>

      <h4>Your Personal Information</h4>
      <div class="row">
        If you would like access to the personal information RoboCent has on file, please send an email to info@RoboCent.com. You may also access or update this information on our platform. Your information is stored while your account is active and as long as necessary for RoboCent to comply with legal obligations.
      </div>

      <div class="divider_space_thin"></div>

