        Your security is of the utmost importance to RoboCent -- we routinely review and test our security procedures to ensure your information is safely and securely stored. All credit card and billing transactions are processed and stored on a third-party vendor, Stripe.com, which has the best security reviews and procedures in the industry. While RoboCent is not responsible for Stripe's security procedures, you should have the confidence in knowing that we have taken all reasonable precautions to ensuring your financial information is kept safe.
        <br/><br/>
